reviews: Excellent bags, good variety I'm sizes, the big one fit my winter coat nicely.
Seemed I was not the first to have this product. My daughter's came with a tag on the zipper nicely put I. The box mine was not so. The zipper maybe an issue, has a ripple in it. Disappointed

Great product, better than the original ring. Loved the different coloured rings. I didn't notice an odour after cooking like I do with the original one. So happy I gave 2 to my daughter. Great product!

Good product, did a great job on clean my grand children's mess. Not sure how good it will work on pet hair but it's a handy item to have in my vehicle. The cord was nice and long. Glad I bought this, it's convenient and after a few uses it would have paid for its self.

I did alot of research before I bought this product, so glad I did. Excellent product, holds my s10 plus with a heavy case perfectly. It's easy to install however I found the ball swivel to be tight but it's good knowing my phone won't be rotating in the holder. I went over several pot holes and bumps and it was solid in the holder. Worth while purchase. Just remember it does block your air vent so be mindful about turning on the heater or AC it may effect the phone. Overall very happy.
Unfortunately, after a couple of months they broke. They were good but not durable enough for children.

Wow, this is a beast! I was surprised to see how big it was, this is not for someone with small hands unless you workout. Really happy with this case, the price is really worth it. Let's hope the red on the metal frame doesn't chip. Only thing I find strange, why is the power key at the side indented and the volume buttons stick out?

review_title: Excellent product, exactly what I wanted
reviews: Anker did it again, another fantastic purchase, I will be buying my daughter one
Terrible quality, broke after 5th use.
Great book!! Parents be mindful.. this books seems to be slightly inappropriate with regards to the donkeys differences. However my daughter LOVES it. We use our Alexa tons lay the song for us!
This product is amazing!! I have natural 4C curly hair, and my daughter is bi racial. This product works WONDERS in our hair! Definitely a must buy!
The cot is good, however it doesn’t fully lay flat.. still a great bed tho!! We used it for sleepover with grandma

Another excellent product from Unicorn Beetle. I bought this for my LG and now my Samsung. Quality product, light weight but very sturdy. This does not come with a screen protector the s10 comes with a preinstalled one. Kick stand is an added bonus, wish it didn't come with the belt holder I have no use for it. Excellent product makes my phone feel really protected. I have had my LG case for 2 years and still looks like brand new.

I'm a proud supporter of Ankor products and this one didn't disappoint. Its much smaller than I had imagined but it's does charge super fast. Overall, it is doing what I wanted, next time I will buy a bigger one so I can charge more than one phone at a time but for the price is great.

Another wonderful product from Soundcore, I really like the quality and price of their products. The base is not bad, took off the headset and my ears are still vibrating. It's a good quality product for the money. I have a Ankor speaker so I know the battery life in this headset is going to last.
Fantastic product, works much better than more expensive systems. If you want peace and quiet and knowing it's soothing for your baby buy this product.
Useless

review_title: Good product, does what I expected
reviews: Good product, adds weight to the tablet but it is protecting it so you must expect that, just wish it came with a built in screen protector I would have given it 5 stars. The colour is great, fast delivery.
This product was used, I would not allow my children to use this car seat it's too flimsy.
Excellent product, really sturdy and looks really nice - has an expensive look to it, it's longer than I thought and looks good in my hallway. It took me 8 minutes to set it up.

review_title: Are you looking for a deep tissue massage? This is it!
reviews:
If you are looking for a deep massage this is the right product.
Pros
Quiet, efficient, gets deep down into the muscle tissue, very reasonably priced for such a good quality product, feels great, like it's doing something good.
Cons
heavy, the heat is luke warm
Overall it's a good quality product, let's see how long it will last.
The dollar store sales the same product, I find these were cheap quality, very small and waste of money.
I have a super size head and this hat fits nicely, lots of room at the top, good quality warm hat.

Wow!! This is the most amazing good quality head band I have ever bought. I will never use a scarf again, the designs are amazing, where do I get more??? They are so good I gave my daughter 3, we are so in love with them. Worth every cent, I am sooooo delighted with this product.
Great little toy

review_title: What was it suppose to do?
reviews: Don't waste your money, after using it for a week it did not alleviate any of the symptoms it said it could do. It constantly moves so you end up fixing it.

review_title: Google Mini is not in Echo's league
reviews: Wow! This is an amazing quality product both in sound and quality, the price is exceptional. I bought the Google Mini wish I could send it back, no comparison. I bought two and I am so thrilled I got them both on sale. Don't waste your money on the Mini, it's like comparing apples to oranges. Looooooove this product.
Quality is very good.
AMAZING!! Well worth the money, eaisiest thing I’ve ever used!

review_title: Not bad for the money but lacks bass
reviews:
If your looking something with bass this is not it. It's a good little speaker for the money but It does not compare to Bose or other deep bass speakers. I bought it to take when I travel and it's perfect for that, maybe the newer model has more bass. If you play high pitched songs it's ok but if you are into lounge music and jazz I find it doesn't play the rich deep tones like on my Bose.
It is stylish and compact and I wanted something with long battery life.
Waste of money
Excellent pressure cooker, just hate the smell it absorbs.
Unfortunately I didn't find this product that great, I don't find the suction strong enough, it's an ok product but wouldn't buy it again.
As of January 31, 2019 you can no longer use wii to view Netflix, perfect device, easy to install and picture quality amazing. After installation don't forget to turn your tv setting to HDMI.

Excellent quality, doesn't show finger prints on the back of the case. Nice colour fits perfectly, fits nicely and works well over each button. Screen cover very nice, better than the otter box case I had on it, the blue colour is very stylish. No regrets.
Good quality cords, very good quality for the money.

Absolutely amazing bags, too bad I didn't get the sale price but still worth the money. These bags are far better than the Ikea brand, they are stiff when you first get them but after a few washes they soften up. Very durable, zippers are very strong and life time replacement you can't go wrong. Shipping was super fast.

I got this unit yesterday and used it twice, already I feel a big difference in my knee. I use to have a Dr. Hos but this product is just as good of not better. It's simple to use and delivers a powerful massage on level 4, I would not recommend you go any higher. It's a really good machine for the money. The only reason I'm not giving it a 5 star just wish it came with a little cloth bag to put it in. Use a heating bag before you use it to get maximum efficiency, let's hope it last. Really good product, love that it's portable.
